description:
Since Boo is on the other side, he has lots of friends - both alive and akin. If you need a word of wisdom, he can ask his friends for one. Hope that his friend's word of wisdom will cheer you up, make your day, or even motivate you!

How to use?
- Just click anywhere on the artwork, and Boo will go to someone and ask for their famous word of wisdom!
